<p><em><a href="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/you-and-me/You%20and%20Me.mp3">You and me</a></em></p>
<p><em>Should take a trip across the galaxy</em></p>
<p><em>And feel the breaking waves of our own energy</em></p>
<p><em>And everything will come together</em></p>
